OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1781524080
OL,3,CFox cubs caught in goal netting sparks
OL,4,Cwarning from RSPCA during World Cup
OL,6,FThe RSPCA is urging football fans to
OL,7,Fpack away goal netting, with the World
OL,8,FCup expected to inspire people to get
OL,9,Foutside for a kickabout.
OL,11,FAny netting that is left outside can
OL,12,Fpose a serious risk to wildlife,
OL,13,Fparticularly in the summer when young
OL,14,Fanimals are exploring.
OL,16,FThe RSPCA is highlighting the story of
OL,17,Ftwo fox cubs that were found with goal
OL,18,Fnetting wrapped tightly around their
OL,19,Fbodies.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
