FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1781524080
OL,3,CFox cubs caught in goal netting sparks
OL,4,Cwarning from RSPCA during World Cup
OL,6,FThe netting had caused bruising and
OL,7,Fswelling.
OL,9,FThey were both treated at a wildlife
OL,10,Fhospital before being returned to
OL,11,Ftheir den.
OL,13,FAnimal Rescue Officer Ellie Barnes-
OL,14,FWilson Ellie said: "People often don't
OL,15,Frealise how dangerous loose netting
OL,16,Fcan be for wildlife. Fortunately,
OL,17,Fthese cubs were incredibly lucky to
OL,18,Fhave been found in time.
OL,26,@vD@TOU
