FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1781524080
OL,3,CFox cubs caught in goal netting sparks
OL,4,Cwarning from RSPCA during World Cup
OL,6,F"It's great that so many people will
OL,7,Fbe spending time outdoors after being
OL,8,Fmotivated by the World Cup and their
OL,9,Fsporting heroes on TV. But, after the
OL,10,Fgames are done, the netting always
OL,11,Fneeds to go away."
OL,13,FThe charity says that deer are
OL,14,Fparticularly susceptible to stress
OL,15,Fand, in many cases, tragically do not
OL,16,Fsurvive for very long after being
OL,17,Ftrapped due to stress-induced muscle
OL,18,Fbreakdown.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
