PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1781524080
OL,3,CFox cubs caught in goal netting sparks
OL,4,Cwarning from RSPCA during World Cup
OL,6,FRSPCA supporter and iconic sports
OL,7,Fbroadcaster, Kirsty Gallacher,
OL,8,Fsupports the RSPCA's warning, adding
OL,9,Fthat the issue is an important
OL,10,Freminder, particularly during major
OL,11,Ffootball tournaments.
OL,13,FShe said "Throughout my career in
OL,14,Fsports broadcasting, I have seen how
OL,15,Fmajor football tournaments bring
OL,16,Fpeople together like nothing else.
OL,26,@uD@JOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
