OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1781524080
OL,3,CFox cubs caught in goal netting sparks
OL,4,Cwarning from RSPCA during World Cup
OL,6,F"With the World Cup set to captivate
OL,7,Fmillions of fans this summer - and
OL,8,Fwith England and Scotland both
OL,9,Finvolved - there'll also be loads of
OL,10,Fpeople heading out for a kick about,
OL,11,Fincluding in back gardens, local parks
OL,12,Fand green spaces.
OL,14,F"But when the game is done, it's
OL,15,Fimportant to remember that goal
OL,16,Fnetting can sadly be really dangerous
OL,17,Ffor wildlife if left out or not put
OL,18,Faway properly.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1781524080
OL,3,CFox cubs caught in goal netting sparks
OL,4,Cwarning from RSPCA during World Cup
OL,6,F"Animals, particularly young fox cubs,
OL,7,Fare naturally curious and can easily
OL,8,Fbecome trapped as they explore their
OL,9,Flocal areas.
OL,11,F"Packing nets and equipment away after
OL,12,Fuse is such a simple thing we can do,
OL,13,Fbut it really can make all the
OL,14,Fdifference in protecting the wildlife
OL,15,Fsharing our local communities, while
OL,16,Fstill enjoying the beautiful game.
OL,18,F"It's a small act that can make a big
OL,19,Fdifference for our nation's wildlife
OL,20,Fthis summer."
OL,26,@nD@AOU|D@MO]
